<li>Apply the conversion formula to convert CFM to LPS: Multiply the CFM va=
lue by 0.471947.
<ul>
<li><strong>Example Calculation</strong>:
<ul>
<li>LPS =3D 100 CFM =C3=97 0.471947 =3D 47.1947 LPS</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Round the Result</strong>: Depending on your requirements, roun=
d the result to a practical number. In this case, 47.2 LPS serves as a suit=
able approximation.</li>
</ol>
